name: Shontell R McClain
bio: Mother of Sierra, Lauryn, China Anne and Gabriel McClain; Wife of MJ McClain; woman of GOD and writer

social_posts.post_text: So Mommie got a bunch of pics together and forgot to hit the button in the middle of cooking on JANUARY 9th so here I am on 1/11 late as hell to say Happy Birthday Thing 2!!!!! I LOVE YOU MWBLT…. Only those closest and dearest know your REAL nickname!!!!!!!! 😘🤣😆🎂❤️

My Michael, Happy 50th Birthday my Love!!!! 31 years ago we met and fell in love. We have celebrated more birthdays together than we have apart and they have been the happiest three decades + one year of my life. I remember baking you a birthday cake for your 20th birthday and the first cake fell so I made you another one because I wanted it to be perfect just like your immeasurable love and respect for me. I am truly the most blessed woman I know because I get to call you my very own. My spiritual soul mate, my lover, my best friend, the one and only true love of my life, my boyfriend, my hubby, my prayer partner, my baby daddy (lol) of our extraorextraordinary adult children, my business partner, my laughter, my heart, my entire world. You always lead me back to who GOD designed me to be and you spoil me rotten with your love. HAPPY 50TH BIRTHDAY HUBBY of mine!!!!!!!!!! Let’s do 50 more years together and leave our mark on the world by glorifying our GOD/Father in Heaven.

Happy Birthday to my first baby… my Angel sent straight from Heaven.  My gift from GOD.  Where do I begin?  How do I put into words what you mean to me?  I’m a writer and yet I find myself at a loss for words to adequately express all that you truly mean to me.  I thought I knew love until I saw your beautiful face.  A face I’ve grown more and more attached to with each passing day.  You hold a special place in my heart Sisi.  Because of you, I’m inspired to become the best version of myself.  Everyone you encounter walks away feeling better about themselves and the infinite possibilities of who they could become through a divine relationship with GOD.  You are love.  You don’t know anything else and yet you continue to somehow grow better with each passing day.  I’m not only a better woman because you are my daughter, but I’m a better everything because you chose to enter this life through me.  I know GOD loves me because I was transformed for the better since March 16th, 1994…. The day I became your Mommie.  Love you SO much and thank you for choosing me to be your mother.  Happy Birthday 🐞…😘🥹🥰🎉🎂
@iamjamiefoxx we are praying for your recovery!!! Hang in there!!! Hugs 🙏🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾

To the best Mom a woman could ever ask for.  Mom, I would choose you a million times over to be my mother again for the 26 years I had you.  I miss you so much today, tomorrow and for the rest of my life.  Your four grandchildren are all adults now and we talk about you all the time.  Happy Heavenly Mother’s Day!!!
Congrats Mommie @chriseanchriseanchrisean on the birth of your son!!! Praying you are both doing well and will continue to lift you both up in prayer. 🙏🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾🥺😘😘🥰❤️❤️

@chinamcclain HAPPY BELATED BIRTHDAY SWEETHEART!!!! We had our phones away for your birthday celebrating so I didn’t post Aug 25th.  I want you. To know every single time i spend time with you, i feel better about myself.  You are truly the most fascinating person I’ve ever known.  You are an amazing daughter and a great friend.  We are still going on your dream trip very soon.  Adore you and love you beyond words. -Mommie
Me today at 52!!! Makeup by my baby @laurynmcclain
HAPPY BIRTHDAY CUJO!!! You have been with us for 13 years and I pray we have you for 13 more!!! I love you my Libra Pooch!!!!
